entries.title_d: Destroy the Coynite Mothership inside of the Dathomir system. It is time for you to show the Coynite what it means to cross the Empire. We have a lock on the Coynite Mothership and you are to destroy it and all that fly with her.
entries.title: Dathomir System: Destroy the Coynite Mothership
entries.quest_target_d: Intercept and destroy the Coynite Mothership.
entries.quest_location_d: Remain in the Dathomir system and intercept the Coynite Mothership.
entries.quest_escort_d: Destroy the Coynite escort fighters as well as the Coynite Mothership.
entries.failed_escape: The mothership has eluded destruction. We are most unpleased with your performance. Return to your superior and make a report on this blunder.
entries.destroy_escort: We still detect some of the escort vessels active. Send a clear message to our enemy and destroy them as well.
entries.assassinate_success: Very nice, pilot. You are a credit to the Empire. Return to your superior and make a full report.
entries.arrival_phase_2: Vessel located attempting to leave system. Destroy that ship and all escorts before it is able to make the jump.
entries.arrival_phase_1: Stand by for nav coordinates to the command vessel.
